Basics of Java (Variables, Data Types, Operators)

Control Flow (Loops, Conditional Statements)

Functions & Methods

Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)

Exception Handling

Collections Framework

File Handling

Multi-threading

Advanced Java Concepts
